# Docsify Conventions

## Structure
- `docs/` is the docs root; `index.html` is the entry point
- `README.md` = home page; `path.md` or `path/README.md` for other pages
- `_sidebar.md` defines navigation

## index.html Config
- Use `loadSidebar: true` for sidebar navigation
- Set `name` for the site title
- Pin CDN to `@4` for stable updates (e.g. `docsify@4`)

## Sidebar Format (_sidebar.md)
```markdown
* [Label](path)
  * [Nested](path/nested)
```

## Mermaid Diagrams
Use fenced code blocks with `mermaid` language tag.
